SUMMARY:Easter Vigil & Lighting of the Easter Fire
DESCRIPTION:Easter Vigil and Lighting of the Easter Fire\nSaturday\, April 4\, 2026 | 7:30 PM (streamed)\nThis is the first and central liturgy of Easter. Beginning Saturday evening in holy darkness out of which the Easter fire is kindled and candles are lit\, we recount from our scriptures the saving works of God. Click here to visit our streaming services page.
