SUMMARY:Eggstravaganza Family Easter Egg Hunt
DESCRIPTION:Our time together will begin with a few words of reflection and song\, followed by the joyful search for Easter eggs! A color-coding system is used to ensure that children of all ages have fun hunting for eggs hidden just for them. Children are asked to bring their own basket. All children must be accompanied by an adult.
